customPrimary:
Fire rate increases with consecutive shots, theoretically peaking at %s maximum standard rate. Rate bonus resets upon weapon retraction;

Sustained maximum-rate firing for %s causes barrel %s warping from overheating. Brief %s ceasefire allows thermal dissipation;
Retracting the weapon triggers self-replacement mechanisms, clearing existing penalties.

Installing %s grants additional %s maximum firing capacity.

customAncillary:
When its weapon group is deselected or autofire disabled, the weapon auto-retracts to reload, replenishing %s~%s rounds into the magazine over %s;

If ammunition falls below %s, press %s to purge remaining rounds and force immediate retraction-reload cycle.
